These plots(x is LenderYield, y is EstimatedEffectiveYield, faceted by ProsperScore) clearly show that, generally LenderYield has a positive ratio relationship with EstimatedEffectiveYield, and EstimatedEffectiveYield will decrease a little with ProsperScore’s increasing.

Reflection

For this project, my most siginificant obstacle is to find what is the main feature. After investigating of the data’ meaning, I decide EstimatedEffectiveYield as the main feature.

Then, by bivariate and multivariate exploration, I find generally LenderYield has a positive ratio relationship with EstimatedEffectiveYield, and EstimatedEffectiveYield will decrease a little with ProsperScore’s increasing.
